
<item rdf:about='http://www.ietf.org/internet-drafts/draft-yusef-sipcore-sip-authn-01.txt'>
    <title>"Third-Party Authentication for Session Initiation Protocol (SIP)", Rifaat Shekh-Yusef, Christer Holmberg, Victor Pascual</title>
    <link>http://www.ietf.org/internet-drafts/draft-yusef-sipcore-sip-authn-01.txt</link>
    <description>This document defines an authentication mechanism for SIP, that is based on the OAuth 2.0 and OpenID Connect Core 1.0 specifications, to enable the delegation of the user authentication to a dedicated third-party IdP entity that is separate from the SIP network elements that provide the SIP service.</description>
    <dc:date>2017-03-09T08:00:00-00:00</dc:date>
</item>
